9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 13=

11
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:43,560
Wait!

12
00:00:49,000 --> 00:00:49,880
Today is

13
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:52,679
my wedding day with Prince Xuanlie.

14
00:00:58,439 --> 00:00:59,399
(She can't do this.)

15
00:00:59,759 --> 00:01:01,439
(She'll ruin my assassination plan.)

16
00:01:02,079 --> 00:01:03,000
Princess Anhe,

17
00:01:03,119 --> 00:01:06,400
Xuanlie chose me in the end.

18
00:01:13,319 --> 00:01:14,040
Your Majesty,

19
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:16,200
I'm willing to give up
the Northern Army.

20
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,400
I only wish

21
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:19,159
to be Xuanlie's consort.

22
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:20,480
Xuanlie,

23
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:23,760
do you want Muye Luomei as your consort

24
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:25,920
to rightfully seize military power,

25
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:28,239
or become an idle prince

26
00:01:28,359 --> 00:01:29,799
for a Xichu orphan girl?

27
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,760
It's your choice.

28
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,640
Mei Lin,

29
00:01:40,480 --> 00:01:42,120
if you still want a place by his side,

30
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,680
why not get down on your knees
and beg me?

31
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:46,640
Maybe I'll show mercy

32
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,760
and let you stay by Prince Xuanlie

33
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,319
to wash his feet as his concubine.

34
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,400
He chose you?

35
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,239
More like you're abusing your power.

36
00:01:53,319 --> 00:01:54,799
If you hadn't forced him,

37
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,439
Prince Xuanlie

38
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,680
wouldn't have broken our promise.

39
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,640
Forced him with power?

40
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,480
Then let me tell you this.

41
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,560
Xuanlie's consort can only be me.

42
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,039
You're just a slave from a fallen state.

43
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:15,280
Just be good
and enjoy your concubine life.

44
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:17,960
(If that's the case,)

45
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:20,080
(then let's all perish together!)

46
00:02:20,840 --> 00:02:22,599
I'll see who dares make her a concubine!

47
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:27,960
Prince Jinghe.

48
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,639
Prince Jinghe.

49
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,759
Your Highness.

50
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,000
Prince Jinghe stood up.

51
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:54,159
Weren't his legs...

52
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,639
I will

53
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,919
marry Mei Lin as my consort.

54
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:10,639
Jinghe,

55
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,319
if your legs haven't healed,

56
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,520
don't push yourself.

57
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:16,680
Or you'll end up crawling.

58
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,080
Xuanlie,

59
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,680
it's your big day today.

60
00:03:20,639 --> 00:03:22,719
Don't worry about me.

61
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,919
Even in death,

62
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,400
I'll never let go of your hand.

63
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:38,919
Let's go.

64
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,439
What is even happening?

65
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,479
Exactly.

66
00:03:49,879 --> 00:03:51,439
Watch them closely.

67
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,400
Sure.

68
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,800
(You got lucky today.)

69
00:03:54,719 --> 00:03:56,800
(But I'll make sure you die someday.)

70
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,319
You shouldn't have done that in...

71
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,199
Don't start.

72
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,520
I know

73
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,080
you'd kill him during the wedding.

74
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:11,000
But Muye Luomei made her move.

75
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:12,840
If I hadn't stepped in,

76
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:14,599
your life would've been at risk.

77
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,160
I thought

78
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,160
that was part of your plan.

79
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,519
Believe it or not,

80
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,639
I've summoned

81
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:32,879
3,000 secret guards to steal you away.

82
00:04:36,079 --> 00:04:37,759
If you really dared to do that,

83
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,560
I'd kill you.

84
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,680
Does it still hurt?

85
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:51,680
Not anymore.

86
00:04:57,279 --> 00:04:58,600
That's what happens when you mess

87
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,560
with my plans.

88
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,759
As long as your life's at stake,

89
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:06,839
I'll always interfere,

90
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,680
no matter what.

91
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,879
Even if it costs your life?

92
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,360
You'd still do that?

93
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,240
Take my life then.

94
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,860
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

95
00:05:20,110 --> 00:05:23,080
ظآزA celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edgeظآز

96
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,120
(Your Highness,)

97
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,839
(are you worried about me?)

98
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:29,639
I went to him because I was afraid
the poison would kill you,

99
00:05:30,279 --> 00:05:32,639
not because of some deal between us.

100
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,879
Do you even understand that?

101
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,759
(Your Highness,)

102
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,319
(why did you do this?)

103
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,360
Simple. I've fallen for you.

104
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:46,140
ظآزLove crosses every cycle
