112
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,639
Mei Lin, are you alright?

113
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,759
I got your letter.

114
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,600
Letter?

115
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,519
You said there was danger

116
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,519
and told me to rush here.

117
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:29,160
But I never sent you any letters.

118
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:32,279
Your Highness, did you hear that?

119
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,680
She just married
Prince Jinghe yesterday,

120
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:37,519
and now, she's sneaking off

121
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:40,319
to see the hostage prince of Zhao.

122
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,560
If word gets out,

123
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:43,399
the royal family will be humiliated.

124
00:06:45,079 --> 00:06:46,399
Here in public,

125
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,800
she did such an immoral thing.

126
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:49,279
She deserves punishment!

127
00:06:49,639 --> 00:06:50,399
Guards,

128
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:53,199
